room_title: Escape room "USCGC Ingham Escape" by Key West Room Escape in Key West
room_address: USCGC Ingham, 314 Simonton Street Key West, FL 33040
room_description: The United States has placed a border south of Miami, separating the Florida Keys from the mainland. Key West has declared secession from the Union as the Conch Republic. Your team must commandeer the Ingham to defend the newly formed republic.
